      <section eId="sec_33_28_3">
        <num>33-28-3</num>
        <content>
          <p>(Code 1933, § 56-2602.1, enacted by Ga. L. 1979, p. 1407, § 3; Ga. L. 1982, p. 3, § 33; Ga. L. 1990, p. 8, § 33; Ga. L. 1999, p. 536, § 2; Ga. L. 2000, p. 1486, § 1; Ga. L. 2003, p. 577, § 1; Ga. L. 2004, p. 578, § 1; Ga. L. 2019, p. 386, § 84/SB 133; Ga. L. 2020, p. 493, § 33/SB 429.)</p>
          <p>The 2019 amendment,
      effective July 1, 2019, substituted "such contract" for "the contract" throughout subsections (c), (f) and (g); substituted "No" for "In the case of contracts issued on or after July 1, 2000, no" at the beginning of the introductory paragraph of subsection (c); substituted "company shall" for "company will" in paragraph (c)(1) and in the first sentence of paragraph (c)(2).</p>
          <p>The 2020 amendment,
      effective July 29, 2020, part of an Act to revise, modernize, and correct the Code, revised punctuation at the end of paragraph (c)(5).</p>
        </content>
      </section>
